# Never publish secrets — private keys, TLS material, Python bytecode caches.
# (2026-07-22: every "publish signed bundle to cockpit CDN" release commit
# had been sweeping .meshkore/scripts/tls/ + __pycache__ into
# public/reference/cluster/scripts/ along with the legitimate daemon.py +
# daemon.py.sig, leaking daemon.meshkore.com's live TLS private key.)
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pem
*.key
